name: TATA-NEXON
description: The Nexon is a spacious and comfortable SUV that looks good, is equipped with several modern features, and boasts a five-star safety rating. It is also complimented for its ride quality, adequate performance, and high-speed stability.

name: SWIFT
description: The Maruti Suzuki Swift is a popular, compact hatchback known for its fuel efficiency, practicality, and a balance of features and performance

name: TOYAT
description: The Fortuner commands the road with its imposing stance, 4x4 capability, and is known for Toyota's bulletproof reliability. It's a comfortable seven-seater SUV that covers long distances with ease and comfort.

name: THAR
description: This new-gen Thar is still a two-door off-roader but drives reasonably well on the road. Its USP continues with durable construction and a rugged stance despite having a modern design. Both petrol and diesel engine options are powerful, offering 4x4 as well.

name: KIA
description: The Kia Seltos is a more well-rounded package than its pre-facelift model. It has a modern design and offers segment-first features, Level 2 ADAS, and a turbo-petrol engine option, in addition to conventional petrol and diesel variants.

name: TATA-CURVV
description: The Tata Curvv EV is the electric version of the 5-seater SUV-coupe, which is also available with traditional petrol and diesel engines

name: CRETA
description: This mid-size SUV looks premium with consistent quality. Its cabin is spacious and gets modern equipment as well. It drives well whether one chooses the petrol or diesel engine powertrain with smooth gearboxes.

name: Renault Triber

name: RANGE ROVER
description: The Range Rover is a luxury sport utility vehicle (SUV) known for its off-road capability and opulent comfort, with a history spanning over 50 years and evolving through multiple generations.

name: Rolls-Royce Spectre
description: Rolls-Royce is a British luxury carmaker that produces the Phantom, Ghost, Spectre, and Cullinan models. The Rolls-Royce Cullinan is an SUV, while the Spectre is an all-electric car.

name: BMW
description: BMW stands for Bayerische Motoren Werke, which translates to Bavarian Motor Works in English, and is a German multinational manufacturer of luxury vehicles and motorcycles, headquartered in Munich, Bavaria, Germany
